Table 3 presents the classification results on this abstract from the BERT and SciBERT models; true positives in blue and false negatives in red. Using BertViz [25] we analyzed the aggregated attention of all 12 layers of both the models. We observed that keyphrase tokens (\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
